parameters: Clea: In the end, what was that ship?

Captain Melena of the Pirate Crew Pirata: I saw the emblem
on the deck, and it should definitely belong to the Remos
Pirate Crew.

Sophia the priestess: What shines is even more precious than
stars, and what is valuable is even more precious than
life... The legendary pirate crew.

Captain Melena of the Pirate Crew Pirata: I formed the
Pirata Pirate Crew because I was deeply fascinated by their
legend.

Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirate Crew: In the end, I
heard that they were being chased by both the Empire and
Tarasa, and sank without being able to replenish their
supplies...

Mage Relm: I might have made an incredible discovery... If
only I could investigate that ship, I would definitely
become an advanced sorceress!

Tailor Neuro: I will prepare a swimsuit suitable for the
future advanced sorceress! I had such an amazing experience,
I will create a masterpiece!

Tailor Neuro: I'll return to the Beach Lepton tailor shop,
so make sure to come visit me on your journey, even if it's
just along the way!

Captain Agua: This is the area where the red coral reef is
located. So, shall I hear the pirates' secret plan?

Captain Melena of the Pirate Crew: This is our secret
weapon!
Mage Relm: W-Where did you get this!?

Captain Melena of the Pirate Crew: That's a good question,
the correct answer is that I am a pirate!
Thief Nora: Blue crystal... Is this something amazing?

Mage Relm: This device was developed after the war with the
neighboring country Tarasa. It was created with the purpose
of retrieving sunken treasures from the seabed.

Mage Relm: However, there is a major flaw and it needs to be
discarded immediately... No way!

Priestess Sophia: The reason the pirate ship was attacked at
that time was because of this device... Is this the correct
answer?

Captain Melena of the Pirate Crew: The cursed crown may be
the cause, but when we use this, for some reason, sea
creatures gather around!

Captain Melena of the Pirate Crew: Well, now that you know
this, shall we use it?
Clea: Understood, let's go to the seabed with this.

Pirate Captain Melena: Whoa! As expected of the Adventurer's
Guild, quick decision-making!

Clea: Of course, it's for the request, but this time it's
also for the sake of our friend.
Thief Nora: Clea-san... Thank you very much!

Pirate Captain Melena: Please change into lighter clothing
as much as possible. We will prepare for the operation of
the device.

Captain Agwa: When you want to return to the Fotizona Port,
let me know.
Captain Agua: Shall we return to the Fotizona Port?
Captain Agua: Understood, feel free to call me anytime.

Captain Agua: Let's retreat for now! I'll be at the same
spot in Fotizona Port, so feel free to call me.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Are you really
prepared for the depths of the sea?

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Let me know
when you're ready, until then, I'll be admiring the
swimsuits of these beautiful ladies.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: The sea with
beautiful ladies, it's a pirate's dream come true!

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Aren't you
going to change into a bigger swimsuit, big sis?
Thief Nora: Ah, I don't have it...

Priestess Sophia: Nora-chan, let's wear the swimsuits that
I'm taking care of.

Clea: I think it's a good idea, since it's a swimsuit for
Nora-san.
Thief Nora: Y-Yes, understood! I'll go change!
Thief Nora: H-How is it... Is it still weird?
Clea: Please have confidence, it really suits you.

Priestess Sophia: It suits you very well. I wonder if we
really need the red coral.

Mage Relm: Those people are perfectionists, so I want to
make something more suitable for Nora-san.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: I'm ready, let
me use the device.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Please think of
it as wearing an air suit. For more details, please ask the
young mage.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Make sure to
come back safely!

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Agua, I'll
leave the weapon preparations to you. A bunch of monsters
are approaching.

Captain Agua: I'm not helping you, I'm helping them. Don't
misunderstand.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Haha, you're
being cold to a former crew member.
Captain Agua: Because I used to be a crew member, Melena.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: If it's the
young mage, I understand why you would prefer a lighter
outfit, right?
